Allright, one more post.

::Zardus::

Zardus closes Feline's face plate, unattatching the wires he had attatched. 
He had fully reprogrammed her into an Alliance soldier. If the programming 
was successfull (which is up to you to say, Logo), she would follow his every 
command, and serve the Alliance without fail. He had also programmed her to 
be a bit promiscuous, but not a slut like DevilDuer had asked.

He taps his wrist comp, making sure the connection to the device he had 
implanted, which would clear Feline's programming at his command, was secure.

Zardus picks up the antidote to Reptilica's venom, injecting it into Feline. 
He sits back, waiting for her to wake up.
